{"data":[{"date":"08:43 21/08","title":"HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/21/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>HLV Bahrain kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1\u00a0\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Bahrain ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 20/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, song v\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra lo \u00e2u khi ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Bahrain kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Bahrain kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/089549700_1524748953-20180426_150959.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Olympic Bahrain th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \u201cN\u00f3i chung t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Bahrain \u0111\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Trong tay t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110a ph\u1ea7n h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i sinh n\u0103m 1997, 1998. C\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n sinh n\u0103m 1999 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi sinh n\u0103m 2000. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Olympic Tokyo 2020 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00fa t\u00e2m v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 8 n\u0103m, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD. Khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1, sau c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Thanh Trung. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 ASIAD. \u0110i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 \u2018\u0111\u00e0n anh\u2019 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra 19 gi\u1edd 30 ng\u00e0y 23/8 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Patriot Patriot Candrabhaga, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Bekasi, t\u1ec9nh T\u00e2y Java. M\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi-168-194910.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi-168-194910.html\">B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Tr\u1ea7n Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-194906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-194906.html\">T\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Yuta Kamiya - ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban-168-194894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban-168-194894.html\">Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft h\u1ea1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br />\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5715","checkdouble":"194953"},{"date":"07:57 21/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 21/8: Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-218-barca-dinh-ngay-don-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 21/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Real t\u00ednh \"\u0111\u00e1nh \u00fap\" sao tr\u1ebb Dortmund.</strong> Real Madrid \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Julian Weigl c\u1ee7a Borussia Dortmund. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 'Sergio Busquets m\u1edbi', Weigl s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Los Blancos m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Barca t\u00ednh \u0111\u00f3n Pogba v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1. </strong>T\u1edd Don Balon \u0111\u01b0a tin, Barcelona s\u1ebd ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Paul Pogba t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m sau thay v\u00ec ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Pogba v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c M.U ch\u01b0a b\u00e1n anh ngay \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 v\u00ec h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 218 Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 218 Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-188-pogba-duoc-thuong-lon-neu-tu-choi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\"Harry Maguire \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf MU\". </strong>Jonny Evans ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Harry Maguire, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Leicester City. C\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Man United kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 cho nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 m\u00ecnh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nV\u00ec Karius su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson. </strong>Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Loris Karius. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Arsenal nh\u1eafm trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga.</strong> Theo Daily Mirror, Arsenal mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga Igor Diveev c\u1ee7a Ufa. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o U20 Nga v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eed tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Firmino cung khong chiu kem canh voi thanh tich tuong tu Salah\" title=\"Firmino c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/roberto-firmino-day-la-mua-giai-tot-nhat-trong-su-nghiep-cua-toi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Firmino mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Firmino mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.</strong> Trong kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin Roberto Firmino \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a anh n\u1eb1m \u1edf Liverpool khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Dortmund nh\u1eafm \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Barca. </strong>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Barcelona, Paco Alcacer \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Borussia Dortmund xem l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi h\u1ebft k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5714","checkdouble":"194949"},{"date":"07:15 21/08","title":"Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Mo Salah v\u1eabn b\u1ecb th\u1ea7y ch\u00ea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/lien-tuc-toa-sang-mo-salah-van-bi-thay-che.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Salah th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Premier League, Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua West Ham 4-0. L\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f2n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. Anh tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 The Kop c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Salah ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u1ec3 James Milner th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ph\u00fat 45. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 3, l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 11 c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Sadio Mane \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Salah-bi-Klopp-che.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh Salah l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Liverpool. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha b\u1ee9t \u0111i nhanh nh\u1eb9n, anh bu\u1ed9c Aaron Wan-Bissaka ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh s\u00e1t v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Liverpool, Salah v\u1eabn b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u00fa l\u1ed1p b\u00f3ng v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Naby Keita. V\u00e0 HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah v\u1eabn b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng Mo Salah c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng&rdquo;, Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. &ldquo;D\u00f9 sao, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;X\u00e9t tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Salah ph\u1ea3i tham gia nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 7 t\u1edbi, Liverpool s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Brighton t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 3 Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279653\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/8/21/liverpool-crystal-palace-100554359_1200_96.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;urlParent=http://bongdanet.vn/video/crystal-palace-0-2-liverpool-premier-league-ngoai-hang-anh-vong-2-tbd71154\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5713","checkdouble":"194946"},{"date":"07:36 21/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/21/de-bruyne-len-tieng-ve-chan-thuong-mat-nua-mua-giai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool, Sadio Mane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 8 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palace, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&emsp;<br>\r\n- Liverpool gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 34 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Man United (43) v\u00e0 Arsenal (36) l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Sadio-Mane-ghi-ban-cho-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sadio Mane \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Liverpool ch\u1ec9 thua 1 sau 10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i Premier League, th\u1eafng 6 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Palace \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 16 sau 20 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m &ldquo;Big Six&rdquo; t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 (h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Roy Hodgson ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 100 t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng (th\u1eafng 87, h\u00f2a 65).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Wan-Bissaka \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Palace nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1i Premier League (20 tu\u1ed5i, 267 ng\u00e0y).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- James Milner \u0111\u00e3 n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh (48 tr\u1eadn, th\u1eafng 38 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 10).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Milner \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf 13 trong s\u1ed1 15 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Premier League, 9 cho Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi 8 b\u00e0n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m 11m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279653\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/8/21/liverpool-crystal-palace-100554359_1200_96.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;urlParent=http://bongdanet.vn/video/crystal-palace-0-2-liverpool-premier-league-ngoai-hang-anh-vong-2-tbd71154\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5712","checkdouble":"194948"},{"date":"19:24 20/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 20/08: Mourinho s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gi\u00e1ng sinh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-2008-mourinho-se-bi-sa-thai-truoc-giang-sinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 20/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gi\u00e1ng sinh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 2008 MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 2008 MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/hlv-ky-cuu-ly-giai-tai-sao-mu-khong-ung-ho-mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gi\u00e1ng sinh n\u1ebfu M.U ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u1ebft b\u00e1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Lee Sharpe, n\u1ebfu M.U ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn thua Brighton HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gi\u00e1ng sinh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eafm Falcao</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Falcao c\u1ee7a Monaco l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Los Blancos nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi. Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>V\u00ec Chelsea, HLV Sarri nguy\u1ec7n b\u1ecf thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea sau 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Premier League. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111ang d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh ng\u1eebng h\u00fat thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 to\u00e0n t\u00e2m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-maurizio-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chelsea-172-194915.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/hlv-maurizio-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-maurizio-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chelsea-172-194915.html\">V\u00ec Chelsea, HLV Sarri nguy\u1ec7n b\u1ecf thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1</span><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea sau 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Premier League. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111ang d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh ng\u1eebng h\u00fat thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Firmino\" title=\"Firmino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/firmino-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Firmino cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Aaron Ramsey</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Andrew Robertson, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid s\u1eafp chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid ha Getafe 2-0\" title=\"Real Madrid ha Getafe 2-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/goc-nhin-khong-ronaldo-real-madrid-con-vung-vang-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real s\u1eafp chi \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong 2 tu\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch &quot;tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n&quot; John Stones</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi John Stones, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-john-stones-172-194898.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/man-city-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-john-stones.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-john-stones-172-194898.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span><br>\r\nMan City mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi John Stones, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Berbatov l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dimitar Berbatov cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V MU kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5711","checkdouble":"194926"},{"date":"21:28 20/08","title":"C\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 Top 10 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a UEFA","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/cong-bo-top-10-ung-vien-cho-giai-thuong-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-nam-cua-uefa.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Top 10 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t  n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong n\u0103m qua.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Top 10 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t\u00a0 n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, danh s\u00e1ch 10 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n. Trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"10 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"10 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/cong-bo-top-10-ung-vien-cho-giai-thuong-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-nam-cua-uefa.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo, Salah v\u00e0 Modric l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a n\u0103m c\u1ee7a UEFA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ghi 15 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 13 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Champions League gi\u00fap Real l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo c\u00f2n ghi 26 b\u00e0n sau 27 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga, t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMohamed Salah l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi 44 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u00e0o Top 4 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u00c1 qu\u00e2n Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSalah c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf VCK, nh\u01b0ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuka Modric t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann, Lionel Messi, Kylian Mbappe, Kevin De Bruyne Raphael Varane, Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Sergio Ramos l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a UEFA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2011, ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 Messi, nh\u1eefng n\u0103m ti\u1ebfp theo Andres Iniesta (2012), Franck Ribery (2013), Ronaldo (2014), Messi (2015), Ronaldo (2016) v\u00e0 Ronaldo (2017) l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2018 c\u1ee7a UEFA s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 30 th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5710","checkdouble":"194930"},{"date":"23:58 20/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: Gabriel Jesus b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/nong-gabriel-jesus-bi-loai-khoi-dt-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil, ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jesus b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khu v\u1ef1c Nam M\u1ef9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, anh ghi t\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 si\u00eau sao Neymar (6). V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a HLV Tite \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Gabriel-Jesus-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Brazil-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jesus b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Roberto Firmino.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Firmino khi\u1ebfn Jesus b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Brazil s\u1ebd c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 El Salvador, trong danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a HLV Tite kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Jesus. Danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp bao g\u1ed3m Douglas Costa (Juventus), Everton (Gremio), Roberto Firmino (Liverpool), Neymar (Paris Saint-Germain), Pedro (Fluminense) v\u00e0 Willian (Chelsea).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Jesus quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil, ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gabriel Jesus quyet tam canh tranh vi tri voi Fimino\" title=\"Gabriel Jesus quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi F\u1ec9mino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/nong-gabriel-jesus-bi-loai-khoi-dt-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gabriel Jesus quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Firmino</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd m\u1edbi g\u1ecdi cho t\u00f4i v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng vui khi b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i cho Man City v\u00e0 \u0110T Brazil, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf v\u1edbi HLV r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Gabriel Jesus ghi b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-1 c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Aguero v\u00e0 Firmino \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man City v\u00e0 Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a Brazil cho 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 El Salvador</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: </strong>Alisson (Liverpool), Neto (Valencia), Hugo (Flamengo)\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7: </strong>Alex Sandro (Juventus), Dede (Cruzeiro), Fabinho (Liverpool), Fagner (Corinthians), Felipe (Porto), Filipe Luis (Atletico Madrid), Marquinhos, Thiago Silva (Paris Saint-Germain)\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7:</strong> Andreas Pereira (Manchester United), Fred (Manchester United), Arthur (Barcelona), Philippe Coutinho (Barcelona), Casemiro (Real Madrid), Lucas Paqueta (Flamengo), Renato Augusto (Beijing Guoan)\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o:</strong> Douglas Costa (Juventus), Everton (Gremio), Roberto Firmino (Liverpool), Neymar (Paris Saint-Germain), Pedro (Fluminense), Willian (Chelsea)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5709","checkdouble":"194936"},{"date":"18:53 20/08","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Real 2-0 Getafe: Khi Bale d\u1ea7n thay th\u1ebf vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/du-am-real-20-getafe-khi-bale-dan-thay-the-vai-tro-cua-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u La Liga 2018/19 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe, tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Getafe ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111ang d\u1ea7n thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gareth Bale duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Real Madrid vs Getafe Bale thay th\u1ebf vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Real Madrid vs Getafe Bale thay th\u1ebf vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Du-am-Real-Madrid-vs-Getafe-Bale-thay-the-vai-tro-cua-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bale \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y CR7 l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng TBN s\u1ebd suy gi\u1ea3m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng khi si\u00eau sao 33 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 9 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng (trung b\u00ecnh 2,2 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn). \u1ede tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid, d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i song K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng v\u1eabn ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng Real v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Gareth Bale \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid, Bale \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, bao g\u1ed3m 3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBale kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang d\u1ea7n bi\u1ebfn tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Real Madrid b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga 2018/19, Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp Getafe. V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Getafe ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gareth Bale ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3. Bale tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale cua Real\" title=\"Gareth Bale cua Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/gareth-bale-noi-gi-sau-ngay-ra-quan-la-liga-cua-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Bale g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat 15, Bale \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111i tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang. Sau \u0111\u00f3 anh bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3i bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1edbi c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m uy l\u1ef1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Carvajal ch\u00ednh Bale l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David Soria ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng ra. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng Carvajal \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGareth Bale c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho Real Madrid, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3m \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ebft c\u1ee1 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n76 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Bale th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 3 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m (nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n), anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a H\u00e8, Bale ghi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. NHM Real \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi th\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ghi b\u00e0n. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y Ronaldo ra \u0111i, n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a anh. Hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a b\u1eb1ng CR7 nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Bale \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. 11 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 th\u00ec c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 8 l\u1ea7n b\u00f3ng \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh nh\u01b0ng Bale th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 ghi b\u00e0n thay v\u00ec qu\u1ea5y ph\u00e1 \u1edf bi\u00ean. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales ch\u1ec9 ghi 21 b\u00e0n sau 39 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u con s\u1ed1 44 b\u00e0n sau 44 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"bale ronaldo\" title=\"bale ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/11/15/Tien-dao-Ronaldo-sap-duoc-gia-han-hop-dong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bale d\u1ea7n thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, khi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n \u1edf Bernabeu c\u00f2n Bale tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt trung t\u00e2m tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Neymar, Mbappe hay Eden Hazard. HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng bi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Los Blancos thay v\u00ec chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5708","checkdouble":"194922"},{"date":"00:36 21/08","title":"Victor Lindelof b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/victor-lindelof-bat-ngo-tho-lo-uoc-mo-khong-the-tin-duoc.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Victor Lindelof mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi, anh t\u1eebng th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Fabien Barthez, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Victor Lindelof t\u1eebng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Victor Lindelof \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Benfica v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2017. Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Victor Lindelof mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Victor Lindelof mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/victor-lindelof-bat-ngo-tho-lo-uoc-mo-khong-the-tin-duoc.PNG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lindelof t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nNh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Lindelof c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho tin t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Eric Bailly \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nVictor Lindelof mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi, anh t\u1eebng th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Fabien Barthez, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, khi c\u00f2n sinh s\u1ed1ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u00f9ng qu\u00ea t\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. T\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t khu ch\u1ee3 g\u1ea7n khu t\u00f4i s\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 b\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng l\u00fac b\u1ea5y gi\u1edd, m\u1eb9 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 mua cho t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Fabien Barthez\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn gi\u1eefa v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ee9ng trong khung g\u1ed7 h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cKhi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac t\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nBarthez \u0111\u1ebfn M.U n\u0103m 2000 t\u1eeb Monaco, trong h\u01a1n 3 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf anh \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 139 l\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Alex Ferguson. Barthez t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u1edbi Marseille v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1993 v\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1998 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U, Barthez c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i Old Trafford khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Tim Howard.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2002/03, Barthez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Marseille theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2003-04.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5707","checkdouble":"194938"},{"date":"01:02 21/08","title":"HLV Klopp t\u1ee9c \u0111i\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/hlv-klopp-tuc-dien-nguoi-voi-thong-tin-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dejan Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro HLV Klopp s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lovren \u0111ang d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trung v\u1ec7 Dejan Lovren \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Croatia, phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua Ph\u00e1p 2-4.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dejan Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng Croatia v\u1eabn tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dejan Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng Croatia v\u1eabn tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/hlv-klopp-tuc-dien-nguoi-voi-thong-tin-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lovren kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 3 v\u00f2ng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd. Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0y \u1ea3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 g\u1eb7p West Ham.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, Lovren v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. HLV Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 9.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ecf \u1edf b\u1eafp \u0111\u00f9i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong th\u00e1ng 8, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 9\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian Lovren kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u HLV Klopp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Van Dijk v\u00e0 Joe Gomez \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng West Ham 4-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lovren c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 6/9 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i UEFA Nations League v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11 th\u00e1ng 9.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lovren c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-thong-bao-thoi-diem-lovren-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-172-194345.html\" target=\"_blank\">Dejan Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng </span>nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro HLV Klopp s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Lovren m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Klopp ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i thay v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu L\u0110B\u0110 Croatia c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Lovren ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Klopp v\u00e0 Liverpool s\u1ebd ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n. Khi m\u00e0 The Kop \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Lovren ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5706","checkdouble":"194939"},{"date":"06:02 21/08","title":"Liverpool kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 m\u01a1, Klopp v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/liverpool-khoi-dau-nhu-mo-klopp-van-chua-mo-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool. \u00d4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e0n lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Liverpool c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League hay kh\u00f4ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Palace</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay (21/8) trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League. Qua \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH, c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Man City v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp sau b\u1edfi thua k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u2013 b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, The Kop v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua West Ham 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a James Milner v\u00e0 Sadio Mane v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Palace c\u00e0ng ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/HLV-Klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp ch\u01b0a m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool l\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea5y g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c. \u00d4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 1989/90.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u00e0nh th\u1eadt m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d, Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sports khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Liverpool c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Premier League. \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c ch\u1ec9 sau 2 tu\u1ea7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-vong-2-premier-league-201819-372-194933.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-vong-2-premier-league-201819.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-vong-2-premier-league-201819-372-194933.html\">Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool: Si\u00eau Salah tinh qu\u00e1i, The Kop khoan kho\u00e1i</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n song Messi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Premier League 2018/18....</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Naby Keita v\u00e0 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen, HLV Klopp c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00fat nh\u00e1t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u1edbng ngo\u1ea1i. Keita c\u1ea7n c\u1edfi m\u1edf h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat\u201d, Klopp n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Mane. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u00eau m\u1ebfn Keita nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady hay kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian. Keita \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.\u201d<strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5705","checkdouble":"194940"},{"date":"06:25 21/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Man City b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/30/thu-mon-man-city-bat-ngo-dinh-chan-thuong-nang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Claudio Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng Man City v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea9y HLV Pep Guardiola v\u00e0o b\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u00f3c b\u00faa v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Ederson.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nClaudio Bravo \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t g\u00e2n g\u00f3t ch\u00e2n Achilles trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c x\u00e9t nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ec9 ra Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Chile d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi Barcelona v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 5 t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ki\u1ec3m tra chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Claudio Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Claudio Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Claudio-Bravo-dinh-chan-thuong-nang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Claudio Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u1edf g\u00f3t ch\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng qua trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Bravo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 tai n\u1ea1n m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i. Anh vi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng: \u201cKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra. Cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 v\u1eady, c\u00f3 l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00fac kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y mai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00e0i to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a Guardiola</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n Claudio Bravo ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n nh\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 HLV Pep Guardiola. Trong tay \u00f4ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 Ederson. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u00e1n Joe Hart cho Burnley v\u00e0 Angus Gunn cho Southampton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi 20 tu\u1ed5i, Daniel Grimshaw l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Man City l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00fap tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Guardiola s\u1ebd \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u trong vi\u1ec7c xoay tua \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man City m\u00e0 Guardiola \u0111ang \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016, \u00f4ng t\u1eebng th\u1eb3ng tay g\u1ea1t Joe Hart ra kh\u1ecfi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Bravo t\u1eeb Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. 1 n\u0103m sau, Guardiola l\u1ea1i y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00f3 Ederson t\u1eeb Benfica v\u00e0 Man City ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-dong-y-mourinho-man-city-khong-the-mua-dang-cap-172-194850.html\">Guardiola \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd Mourinho: Man City kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-khinh-bi-man-city-va-doi-tien-catxe-dong-phim-172-194838.html\">Mourinho khinh b\u1ec9 Man City v\u00e0... \u0111\u00f2i ti\u1ec1n c\u00e1t-x\u00ea \u0111\u00f3ng phim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/man-city-vs-huddersfield-ngoai-hang-anh-1982018-372-194821.html\">Man City 6-1 Huddersfield (KT): S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Aguero l\u1eadp hattrick, Man xanh \u0111\u00e1nh tennis tr\u00ean Etihad</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-chui-tuc-vi-chan-thuong-cua-de-bruyne-172-194763.html\">HLV Klopp ch\u1eedi t\u1ee5c v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a De Bruyne</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5704","checkdouble":"194941"},{"date":"06:54 21/08","title":"Thua tr\u1eadn, HLV Palace t\u1ed1 Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/21/thua-tran-hlv-palace-to-liverpool-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c James Milner th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Roy Hodgson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sai l\u1ea7m.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Palace</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang v\u00e0o ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Crystal Palace v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Michael Oliver x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Mamadou Sakho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Mohamed Salah trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb c\u1ef1 ly 11m, James Milner \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Liverpool. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y, Palace kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ph\u00fat 75, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Aaron Wan-Bissaka bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Salah ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Roy Hodgson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Roy Hodgson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/HLV-Roy-Hodgson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Hodgson kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1 h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Liverpool kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gia t\u0103ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t. Ph\u00fat 90+3, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng, Salah ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Sadio Mane \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palace.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Hodgson kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Roy Hodgson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn. \u00d4ng c\u00f2n cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00fang ra Palace c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i khi Max Meyer b\u1ecb c\u1ea3n l\u1ea1i tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n\u201d, Hodgson n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201cSakho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng hay va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi ai c\u1ea3. Sau \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3. N\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i. T\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng James Milner ng\u00e3 l\u0103n ra khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng hay t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Max Meyer b\u1ecb Van Dijk ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m khi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-khoi-dau-nhu-mo-klopp-van-chua-mo-vo-dich-172-194940.html\">Liverpool kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 m\u01a1, Klopp v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tham-hoa-thu-mon-chia-tay-liverpool-vao-cuoi-tuan-nay-172-194937.html\">Th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n chia tay Liverpool v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-cu-chi-ra-yeu-to-giup-liverpool-co-the-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-mua-nay-172-194935.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-liverpool-khong-bao-gio-chi-mot-so-tien-lon-mua-neymar-172-194934.html\">Klopp: Liverpool kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua Neymar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-vong-2-premier-league-201819-372-194933.html\">Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool: Si\u00eau Salah tinh qu\u00e1i, The Kop khoan kho\u00e1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-karius-suyt-chut-nua-liverpool-da-khong-the-co-alisson-172-194927.html\">V\u00ec Karius su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5703","checkdouble":"194943"}]}